4 A BILL FOR AN ACT ENTITLED: “AN ACT GENERALLY REVISING BUSINESS LAWS; ALLOWING FOR
5 DOMESTICATION OF LIMITED LIABILITY COMPANIES, PROFESSIONAL LIMITED LIABILITY COMPANIES,
6 LIMITED LIABILITY PARTNERSHIPS, PROFESSIONAL LIMITED LIABILITY PARTNERSHIPS, BENEFIT
7 CORPORATIONS, AND NONPROFIT CORPORATIONS; PROVIDING FOR A PLAN OF DOMESTICATION;
8 PROVIDING FOR APPROVAL OF DOMESTICATION; PROVIDING FOR AMENDMENT OR ABANDONMENT
9 OF A PLAN FOR DOMESTICATION; AND PROVIDING FOR A STATEMENT ARTICLES OF
10 DOMESTICATION; PROVIDING DEFINITIONS; PROVIDING FOR NONEXCLUSIVITY; AND PROVIDING
11 FOR REFERENCES TO EXTERNAL FACTS.”
